  • Constructor Details

    • Student_Course

      public Student_Course(String firstName, String lastName, long id)
      Parameterized Constructor of Student_Course class

      This constructor is used to represent and initialize the student course object.

      Precondition - The value of first name and last name must be a string and the value of id must be a valid long value.
      Postcondition - A student course object is created with the variables set to their parameter values, and enrollment type set to 'C'.
      Parameters:
      firstName - The first name of student course object.
      lastName - The last name of student course object.
      id - The identifier value of student course object.
